{
  "stem": "7069.5",
  "chunk_idx": 18,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were covered with a blanket that was filthy from dried pus, similar things like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my bandage was a paper bandage that lasted about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ah-- two weeks?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two-- two hours, I mean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then it was all soaked through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no stitching at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or either it wasn't available, or they didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was just vulnerable to any kind of infection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's another miracle that it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I talked to my doctor once, who-- who gave me a shot and wiped it off, you know, with-- first with alcohol, with a little needle.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, you know something?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing was wiped off when this thing was done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just cut open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so he says well, those things do happen, he says, you don't always get infected.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I gained my strength.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was able and at one time, even ordered to-- to get a little-- to do a little job, to cut hair somewhere-- some-- for new-arriving prisoners, for which I got a little bowl of soup, which was all fine and wonderful.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was the way I was there, until-- until we finally were ordered out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
